位置已由麥當勞餐廳大堂改為餐廳經理室或員工室；<br />\n<br />\n3. 市民如欲透過麥當勞餐廳將充電池交與充電池回收計劃，可直接與餐廳職員聯絡；<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wastereduction.gov.hk/tc/workplace/rechargebattery_detail.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wastereduction.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fworkplace%2Frechargebattery_detail.htm&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=feb0746b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wastereduction.gov.hk/tc/workplace/rechargebattery_detail.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3b002f0fab876803b10e74e3e6f493a6c37e831c","tid":1015743,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c6b8f06c2172ccbd14be6c79d38a5d85cbff6321","tid":1015743,"uid":15815,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:31:26.000Z","msg":"慳電膽都係啦，環保撚成日叫人用<br />\n有水銀架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T11:38:40.000Z","msg":"咁可以回收喎&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"70a2bb1adb09369093f2ca0a1ef49ae1804ee8b4","tid":1015743,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4596ae3d0ec59acf50fc46a79861f849221a4b96","tid":1015743,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T11:26:00.000Z","msg":"而家去老麥直接比個經理就得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T11:39:47.000Z","msg":"都係亂咁劈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知港督府門口收唔收？？？"},{"pid":"e5c640c92e9315ac3715f310bef5809ae016c4fc","tid":1015743,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T11:45:53.000Z","msg":"題外話，街邊垃圾筒如有含水銀光管、慳電膽等，一般清潔工都係就咁扑爛方便處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18419ac9e7d6bca9e3fa752b32a6bd0d216cecc","tid":1015743,"uid":36073,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T14:27:21.000Z","msg":"屌你香港回收真係垃撚圾<br />\n已經親眼睇著屋苑個回收箱係廢，朝朝見清潔工入黑膠袋丟入垃圾房<br />